Veriff's Privacy Notice
Thank you for taking the time to familiarize yourself with Veriff‚Äôs (Veriff O√ú and Veriff Brazil Ltda., hereinafter ‚Äú
Veriff
‚Äù, ‚Äú
we
‚Äù, ‚Äú
